307
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:38,730
Ah, yes. Especially that one short guy is really amazing.

308
00:30:38,730 --> 00:30:40,910
An expert knows other experts.

309
00:30:40,910 --> 00:30:45,210
Earlier, he came to me and asked about Twin Dragons of the East and stuff.

310
00:30:45,210 --> 00:30:47,880
That one short guy...

311
00:30:48,810 --> 00:30:53,600
Master Hong, stay here as well and watch over Moo Hyul.

312
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:57,340
Can I do that?

313
00:30:57,340 --> 00:30:59,750
I don't know what it's like in Goryeo's time

314
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:02,280
but the best swordsman in the new country, Joseon,

315
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:05,410
has to be this guy, Moo Hyul.

316
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:10,880
Can you do it?

317
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:14,250
The warriors here,

318
00:31:14,250 --> 00:31:16,810
I will completely defeat them all.

319
00:32:07,290 --> 00:32:09,410
Lee Seong Gye eventually

320
00:32:09,410 --> 00:32:12,340
ordered your execution.

321
00:32:12,340 --> 00:32:14,470
Tomorrow,

322
00:32:14,470 --> 00:32:17,030
an officer will come here.

323
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:19,190
I

324
00:32:20,060 --> 00:32:22,700
put a dot in the character for Wang

325
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:24,730
and changed my last name to Oak.

326
00:32:26,330 --> 00:32:28,550
You will also go, right?

327
00:32:29,950 --> 00:32:32,360
If I say that I want to live,

328
00:32:33,010 --> 00:32:36,050
she will have to keep fighting

329
00:32:36,050 --> 00:32:38,190
and will die in the end.

330
00:32:39,780 --> 00:32:42,800
Your Highness, come eat.

331
00:32:56,780 --> 00:32:59,220
It was cooked deliciously.

332
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:05,200
If you're going to the market, I have a favor to ask.

333
00:33:06,290 --> 00:33:08,050
Please bring me that.

334
00:33:08,050 --> 00:33:09,370
Sure.

335
00:33:09,370 --> 00:33:12,410
Then, please eat while I'm away.

336
00:33:14,690 --> 00:33:17,790
I will make you a really good dinner.

337
00:33:19,820 --> 00:33:21,400
Yoon Rang.

338
00:33:26,250 --> 00:33:28,110
Thank you.

339
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:51,510
You were keeping something for His Highness, right?

340
00:33:51,510 --> 00:33:52,860
Yes.

341
00:33:56,450 --> 00:33:58,280
It's this.

342
00:34:01,260 --> 00:34:04,780
Isn't this a letter?

343
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:06,160
Yes.

344
00:34:06,830 --> 00:34:08,860
Please read it.

345
00:34:16,750 --> 00:34:18,690
Meeting the beautiful you...

346
00:34:18,690 --> 00:34:24,090
Before I became king, I spent time as if in a dream.

347
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:27,900
My farewell to you really

348
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:30,770
hurts, but

349
00:34:30,770 --> 00:34:32,860
Rang,

350
00:34:32,860 --> 00:34:35,320
even if it's just you, you have to live.

351
00:34:56,250 --> 00:35:00,480
Prince Jeong Chan, Wang Yo acted against the law

352
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:05,280
and many people have left you due to your incapability to manage the country,

353
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:08,530
so you were dethroned by the heavens. Also,

354
00:35:08,530 --> 00:35:13,980
since the heavens have changed, for the stability of the country and safety of the royal family,

355
00:35:13,980 --> 00:35:16,560
Receive your punishment.

356
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:32,840
Rang, like that time when you said you'll fight by my side,

357
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:35,720
I would have told you to run away.

358
00:35:35,720 --> 00:35:37,640
But

359
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:42,040
in any case, I am

360
00:35:42,040 --> 00:35:45,440
the last king of Goryeo which was passed down through the Wang family for 500 years.

361
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:48,560
In the end of the last king,

362
00:35:48,560 --> 00:35:51,320
he shouldn't run, right?

363
00:35:52,830 --> 00:35:58,140
If you go to the paper goods shop in Daerim Marketplace at Gaegyeong, Mr. Oak will be there.

364
00:35:58,140 --> 00:36:02,890
I already told them so you can stay there.

365
00:36:03,820 --> 00:36:08,840
You must not have bad thoughts

366
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:11,490
like ending your own life.

367
00:36:12,750 --> 00:36:17,470
Go find your life now.

368
00:36:18,220 --> 00:36:21,040
You have to do that for me to also

369
00:36:21,040 --> 00:36:24,110
comfortably rest in the afterlife.

370
00:37:36,220 --> 00:37:37,860
Hanyang (after transfer of capital)

371
00:37:37,860 --> 00:37:39,810
It's a petition for impeachment.

372
00:37:44,500 --> 00:37:46,610
Leave out Lord Hong Ak Joon.

373
00:37:46,610 --> 00:37:47,820
Pardon?

374
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:50,490
He is a close member to Lord Sam Bong.

375
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:54,840
There will be promotions soon, in the Office of Inspector General.

376
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:59,560
If you do that, I will put in a good word to him for you.

377
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:05,650
Yes. I will do so.

378
00:38:09,830 --> 00:38:12,310
Go out the back door.

379
00:38:12,310 --> 00:38:14,630
Pardon? The back door?

380
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:24,660
What is the inspector general?

381
00:38:32,190 --> 00:38:35,510
While inspecting the officials' corruption and illegal activities,

382
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:38,940
even if there was a royal command, if you think of it as the right thing to do

383
00:38:38,940 --> 00:38:42,890
you must be prepared to exchange your life for that righteousness.

384
00:38:42,890 --> 00:38:47,460
But you can't even withstand my authority, so you just succumb to it?

385
00:38:48,850 --> 00:38:50,640
Also, all of you

386
00:38:50,640 --> 00:38:54,040
are the first ever government officials of the new country Joseon.

387
00:38:55,610 --> 00:38:59,990
The principles and discipline you guys set will have an effect for hundreds of years to come.

388
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:03,410
If we are not able to set those things right,

389
00:39:03,410 --> 00:39:07,040
this country's officials will also be like Goryeo's officials,

390
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:10,420
who were vampires that sucked the blood out of the people.

391
00:39:11,380 --> 00:39:13,700
Are you going to be like that?

392
00:39:14,240 --> 00:39:18,520
Will it really be that kind of country again?

393
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:36,820
You became like this while trying to stop His Majesty from seeing the king's historical record?

394
00:39:36,820 --> 00:39:38,460
I'm sorry, Lord.

395
00:39:38,460 --> 00:39:40,570
I will make you

396
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:44,810
a rank 3 official.

397
00:39:44,810 --> 00:39:46,140
Pardon?

398
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:51,090
If you're not this much prepared, all of you can resign.

399
00:39:52,050 --> 00:39:54,520
Even if you have to wear a diaper to withstand it,

400
00:39:54,520 --> 00:39:56,640
the Office of Historical Records

401
00:39:56,640 --> 00:40:00,160
has to record every little detail of the king's words and actions.

402
00:40:00,160 --> 00:40:01,490
Yes, yes.

403
00:40:01,490 --> 00:40:05,750
It's said that the king is only afraid of the writer of the historical records.

404
00:40:05,750 --> 00:40:08,020
the historical records, that you guys write with your lives,

405
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:12,810
will become the discipline of the future generations. Do not ever forget that.

406
00:40:12,810 --> 00:40:14,610
Yes, my Lord.

407
00:40:15,260 --> 00:40:16,850
Leader.

408
00:40:19,860 --> 00:40:22,030
We're back.

409
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:26,510
Today is the first day of students in Seonggyeonggwan. Do you all know that?

410
00:40:26,510 --> 00:40:28,600
Of course.

411
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:32,320
We helped with washing up and organization and also checked attendance.

412
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:37,200
We have also checked on where they would stay after classes.

413
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:38,690
You've worked hard.

414
00:40:38,690 --> 00:40:42,030
Then, eat your meal and I will see you later.

415
00:40:42,030 --> 00:40:44,280
Yes, Leader.

416
00:40:50,060 --> 00:40:52,400
Banchon (Village assisting Seonggyungwan scholars)

417
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:54,130
Hello.

418
00:41:11,330 --> 00:41:14,370
The preparations are going well, right?

419
00:41:19,070 --> 00:41:22,490
You're not experiencing any difficulties, right?

420
00:41:27,190 --> 00:41:31,830
The civil service examination is coming up. You are going to have to prepare ahead of time

421
00:41:31,830 --> 00:41:33,670
Yes, leader.

422
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:42,280
To be honest, as we are commoners,

423
00:41:42,280 --> 00:41:46,320
- to be working with people who used to be slaves in Gaegyeong—
- Gab Boon

424
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:52,800
We are all just Banchon people. Keep that in mind.

425
00:41:52,800 --> 00:41:56,830
I understand, Boon Yi. I mean, Leader.

426
00:42:09,350 --> 00:42:11,960
Ajussi.

427
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,720
Hello.

428
00:42:13,720 --> 00:42:14,980
Is the work alright?

429
00:42:14,980 --> 00:42:19,620
It has been worth the wait to come. I like it.

430
00:42:19,620 --> 00:42:25,200
Oh my. Your handiwork is amazing. Look at that, Leader.

431
00:42:25,200 --> 00:42:27,450
You merchandised with brushes before this, right?

432
00:42:27,450 --> 00:42:32,770
Maeng Soon, you shouldn't ask such questions here.

433
00:42:32,770 --> 00:42:36,600
This tongue. I forgot

434
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:41,700
But, I don't see your younger sibling again.

435
00:42:41,700 --> 00:42:45,370
Yes. My younger sibling is inside doing needlework.

436
00:42:45,370 --> 00:42:47,290
I see.

437
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:55,210
You're here.

438
00:42:56,650 --> 00:42:59,890
You always seem to eat your lunch here.

439
00:42:59,890 --> 00:43:04,640
No matter where I go, there's no place better than our grandmother's.

440
00:43:07,440 --> 00:43:11,630
But you seem to be doing well too.

441
00:43:11,630 --> 00:43:13,660
Is that so?

442
00:43:16,120 --> 00:43:17,660
There is nothing much going on, right?

443
00:43:17,660 --> 00:43:20,980
Of course not. Why would I have anything going on?

444
00:43:20,980 --> 00:43:27,360
But, Leader. Have you received any news about the prince who went to Ming?

445
00:43:29,090 --> 00:43:34,210
No, I haven't heard anything either.

446
00:43:37,120 --> 00:43:41,120
Lord Sam Bong is coming. Ask him for me.

447
00:43:45,260 --> 00:43:47,440
Are you on the way to Seonggyungwan?

448
00:43:47,440 --> 00:43:50,580
Yes. I see you're doing inspection.

449
00:43:51,680 --> 00:43:56,420
I heard that all you do is work all day and all night.

450
00:43:56,420 --> 00:43:58,310
It's a blessing.

451
00:43:58,310 --> 00:44:00,810
I...

452
00:44:02,590 --> 00:44:08,020
Has there been news about the prince who went to Ming?

453
00:44:10,030 --> 00:44:13,150
Not yet.

454
00:44:19,090 --> 00:44:22,680
Do not worry too much. He is a talented person.

455
00:44:22,680 --> 00:44:24,700
Yes, yes.

456
00:44:29,380 --> 00:44:34,980
You're alive, right? Right, Bang Won?

457
00:44:39,050 --> 00:44:45,020
Seonggyungwan

458
00:44:45,020 --> 00:44:48,990
It's tonight. Are you all prepared?

459
00:44:48,990 --> 00:44:53,960
Yes. We will all gather at Jeongryunam tonight.

460
00:44:53,960 --> 00:44:59,340
We're taking the first step today so I'm really filled with emotions.

461
00:44:59,340 --> 00:45:05,530
At last, we are finally having our first gathering. My heart is very eager, but everything is going so slowly.

462
00:45:05,530 --> 00:45:08,130
They say that starting means you're halfway there, my Lord.

463
00:45:08,130 --> 00:45:11,770
This is our doctrine. Can you copy these?

464
00:45:11,770 --> 00:45:14,320
Yes. I understand.

465
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:24,440
You told me everything that happened and things that you heard today, right?

466
00:45:24,440 --> 00:45:28,220
Yes. I've told you everything, Leader.

467
00:45:28,220 --> 00:45:32,260
Yes. Then, you can forget everything now.

468
00:45:32,260 --> 00:45:35,720
Forget everything you told me about.

469
00:45:37,060 --> 00:45:41,130
So are you well now after having used the bathroom?

470
00:46:32,780 --> 00:46:34,210
Give it back.

471
00:46:34,210 --> 00:46:35,150
What are you saying?

472
00:46:35,150 --> 00:46:38,020
The thing that you stole from Seonggyungwan.

473
00:46:38,020 --> 00:46:42,760
What are you talking about? I'm doing a night shift, so I was checking on the lights in Seonggyungwan.

474
00:46:42,760 --> 00:46:44,560
I guess words won't work on you.

475
00:46:44,560 --> 00:46:46,360
Brother!

476
00:46:57,450 --> 00:46:59,810
I see you're in the middle of a conversation.

477
00:47:11,610 --> 00:47:14,010
Everyone, you can go out and tend to your jobs.

478
00:47:14,010 --> 00:47:16,020
Yes.

479
00:47:26,240 --> 00:47:28,220
Baek Jin was caught?

480
00:47:28,220 --> 00:47:33,560
It seems that he went into Seonggyungwan and stole a document. He's currently being held in Banchon.

481
00:47:33,560 --> 00:47:35,520
The investigation bureau has gone too, it seems.

482
00:47:35,520 --> 00:47:37,220
What was the document he stole?

483
00:47:37,220 --> 00:47:41,710
He infiltrated Banchon because Sam Bong has been frequently going to Seonggyungwan.

484
00:47:41,710 --> 00:47:44,700
It's probably something related to Sam Bong.

485
00:48:02,750 --> 00:48:10,600
This place, Banchon, has the shrine of Moon Seong Gong and the Daeseong Shrine.

486
00:48:10,600 --> 00:48:16,150
You know that the royal forces are not allowed in unless it's a royal command.

487
00:48:17,020 --> 00:48:19,480
Isn't the criminal inside Banchon?

488
00:48:19,480 --> 00:48:23,620
We have already caught a suspicious person.

489
00:48:23,620 --> 00:48:26,860
Is that so? Then hurry and hand him over to us.

490
00:48:26,860 --> 00:48:30,850
When we caught him, we realized that he's from Banchon.

491
00:48:30,850 --> 00:48:35,500
As long as it's not the royal command, as the leader, I have the right to deal with it.

492
00:48:35,500 --> 00:48:40,190
You can only arrest him, after I expel him.

493
00:48:41,790 --> 00:48:42,930
So?

494
00:48:42,930 --> 00:48:48,790
He's being interrogated so please wait for a bit.

495
00:48:52,760 --> 00:48:58,580
You wench! Do you think we will just wait here?

496
00:49:01,690 --> 00:49:08,560
