500
00:49:33,370 --> 00:49:38,380
Leader. Why would I do that? I never did that.

501
00:49:38,380 --> 00:49:40,480
Then why did you run?

502
00:49:40,480 --> 00:49:44,390
This man followed me so how can I not run?

503
00:49:44,390 --> 00:49:48,530
No, Boon Yi. That's a lie. I'm sure it's him.

504
00:49:50,800 --> 00:49:54,050
Can I look through your clothes?

505
00:49:54,050 --> 00:49:57,580
Of course. Go ahead.

506
00:49:58,960 --> 00:50:05,770
Brother. If he was hiding something, he wouldn't let me check.

507
00:50:05,770 --> 00:50:12,480
Instead of his clothes, I want to look at his body for a tattoo that we know of.

508
00:50:13,190 --> 00:50:15,820
What kind of suspicions do you have?

509
00:50:24,730 --> 00:50:30,420
From here on, I am asking you as your leader who has power over your life and death.

510
00:50:34,010 --> 00:50:37,690
If you lie about what I'm asking you,

511
00:50:37,690 --> 00:50:41,830
you will be kicked out of Banchon and all of us will forget you.

512
00:50:43,230 --> 00:50:45,950
You will become a dead person to us.

513
00:50:48,530 --> 00:50:52,670
Are you a part of Nameless?

514
00:51:10,590 --> 00:51:12,450
Hold him.

515
00:51:14,350 --> 00:51:17,150
Leader! Leader!

516
00:51:17,150 --> 00:51:18,610
Leader!

517
00:51:26,960 --> 00:51:30,160
All of you, take cover!

518
00:51:44,720 --> 00:51:49,260
