523
00:52:33,850 --> 00:52:37,610
He threw beef jerky?

524
00:52:37,610 --> 00:52:41,290
Beef jerky? Huh?

525
00:52:41,990 --> 00:52:45,710
That person is clearly Gil Seon Mi.

526
00:52:46,540 --> 00:52:49,260
Nameless has appeared again.

527
00:52:49,260 --> 00:52:51,780
In Banchon, at that.

528
00:52:53,720 --> 00:52:57,460
Excuse me, Leader!

529
00:52:57,460 --> 00:52:59,560
See me for a bit.

530
00:53:02,740 --> 00:53:05,320
This was found by coincidence.

531
00:53:07,220 --> 00:53:09,140
Is that so?

